PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Human Resources and Skills Development of RENNIE PIETERMAN of London, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Gary Mooney.
